Sadiya, daughter of former Sokoto Governor, Aliyu Wamakko, is dead It was gathered that the Senator’s child died during the week. Yobe Governor, Mai Mala Buni, sent his condolence of Saturday. Buni’s reaction was contained in a statement by his spokesman, Mamman Mohammed. The APC Caretaker Committee Chairman described the death as a sad loss to the family, friends, relations and the country. Buni beseeched God to forgive her shortcomings and grant her soul eternal rest in Aljannatur Firdausi. He also prayed that God would grant Wamakko and his family the fortitude to bear the passing.